SDLx-Tween version 0.01
======================

NOT READY YET

Will be an XS tween engine in for SDL Perl.

Only built on Linux so far.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    SDL
    XS::Object::Magic

